      • draw

        public void draw(processing.core.PApplet drawer)
        Draws a shape at the previously specified color, strokeWeight, and location
        Parameters:
        drawer - PApplet object that draws the shape
        Precondition:
        drawer settings that are applied before affect the shape, except for the thickness of the line and color
        Postcondition:
        drawer settings after the method is run are as such: fill is the previously specified Color, and strokeWeight is the set strokeWeight
